[text_input text="What should we call you?" var="PlayerName" placeholder="Player"]

Alex: Hey there, {PlayerName}! Good to finally meet you.
Sam: Wait, did you just say... {PlayerName}? No way.

Alex: So, {PlayerName}, ready to see how this thing works?

- Yes, let's go!
    Sam: Hah, knew you'd say that.
    jump end_test
- I have questions first.
    Alex: Fair enough — ask away.
    Sam: Or don't. We'll wait.
    jump end_test

label end_test
Alex: Alright, that's the test loop. Everything's wired up correctly.
Sam: {PlayerName} survives contact with the engine. Nice.